Data note 1:

While the New York City syndromic surveillance system captures 100% of all emergency department(ED) visits in the city (as of 5/1/16, 99% prior to that), the data are not comprehensive as only aproportion of residents seek care in emergency departments. Therefore the data are not exact measures of morbidity.
-Data for the most recent two weeks are not final and are subject to change.
Data note 2: -Geographic data may not add up to citywide count data due to missing location data for some patients.
